reviewText: Pretty good.  Along the lines of Dr Quinn Medicine Woman with perhaps a Canidian twist on the wild west.
About time they released these.. was a very good show that had drama and comedy in it... loved the conflict, too.  Item was as descibed, arrived fast, and was well packed.
My experience with this purchase was every bit as pleasing as my purchase of V.1.  I was in now way dissatisfied with any aspect of this shopping experience.
